# RealStart API Reference (Generated)

**Base URL**: `http://localhost:8000/api/v1`

### 1. Register Public User
**URL**: `http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register`

**Success Response**
Status: `200`
```bash
curl -X POST 'http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"email": "newuser_yjapg2@example.com", "password": "StrongPass123!", "full_name": "New User", "role": "BUYER"}'
```
```json
{
  "id": "57454b2d-dee3-497b-8fef-37ab0f1163a5",
  "email": "newuser_yjapg2@example.com",
  "full_name": "New User",
  "role": "BUYER",
  "is_active": true
}
```

**Failure Response**
Status: `422`
```bash
curl -X POST 'http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register' -H 'Content-Type: application/json'
```
```json
{
  "detail": [
    {
      "type": "missing",
      "loc": [
        "body",
        "email"
      ],
      "msg": "Field required",
      "input": {}
    },
    {
      "type": "missing",
      "loc": [
        "body",
        "password"
      ],
      "msg": "Field required",
      "input": {}
    },
    {
      "type": "missing",
      "loc": [
        "body",
        "full_name"
      ],
      "msg": "Field required",
      "input": {}
    }
  ]
}
```

